#ENGLISH LANGUAGE

tellraw @s[scores={LANGUAGE=1}] {"text":" °-° Walton Jones : ","color":"green","extra":[{"text":"Please, I need some help. I'm currently digging further down near the torrent to find fossils, but it's overrun with a fairly dangerous green slimy life form. I no longer dare to venture there... In short, I'm looking for someone who would be able to scare away these monstrosities. I will offer you some Chronotons in exchange.","color":"dark_aqua"}]}


#CHINESE LANGUAGE

